{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is sort of a rude thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember we were finished eating, and I burped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I did not know what part of my body this sound came from or what it meant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were all a little more naive than today's children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the people about dropped their fork and knife right out of their hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, what do you say?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- what is it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What-- what's it about?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, but one does not burp at the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the first time I knew the word 'burp' even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Had apparently not had the necessity to burp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the next place they parked me-- because I had to get away from there, although that man had bought me nice clothes because he thought I was such a perfect specimen of a German child with the blue eyes and the hair.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN]. 'Froh' means 'glad.' So she had a very sunny disposition.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's probably why they called her that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think her name was Gerda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next person I stayed with briefly was apparently a-- a doctor, a woman doctor who practiced out of her house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she couldn't take heathens, so I had to be baptized before she would let me stay there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Hilde said, yes, go ahead, baptize, whatever it takes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And during this time you had no contact with your parents?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-mm, mm-mm, mm-mm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They heard about me, I know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] But-- and it didn't occur to me-- as long as Hilde said, this is what you're going to do and here's where you're going, I-- I had no sense to be afraid or to think, won't they ever come back?",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
